# query

**Interface Property**

The query string used to perform the autocomplete request.

## Declaration

```swift
query: string;
```

## Discussion

The search query that corresponds to the [doc://com.apple.mapkitjs/documentation/MapKitJS/SearchAutocompleteResponse/results].

## Response

- **results**: The results from an autocomplete request.
